Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:05.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とても大好きで　少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:06.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}でも　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:12.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}止まることができなくて嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:21.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:26.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:32.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:37.96,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}同じにはできないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:49.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心も　未来も　笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:56.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そう　まだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:00.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:04.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:07.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.02,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:13.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:17.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You see what I want tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:28.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠と 儚さと 震える夜もあるけれど
