Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:05.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}实在过于喜欢 同时伴随些许痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:06.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:12.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}由于无法停止已经开始厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:21.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便在重要的你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:32.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}收入眼底的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:37.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可能尽然相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:49.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论心意 未来还是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:56.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}对 还有素未谋面的爱
